03:50.200 --> 03:53.530
- Are those Ay-rabs your family?
- They're customers.

03:53.700 --> 03:57.240
Drink up.
Look, there's no problem.

04:06.540 --> 04:08.290
Yeah, there's no problem.

04:19.829 --> 04:23.500
