09:10.580 --> 09:12.380
Stand down, Mitterrand.

09:15.580 --> 09:17.130
Socialism = Defeat.

09:27.620 --> 09:28.950
Hey, Grand-Guy...

09:29.910 --> 09:33.320
- Give us a hand.
- There's only 3 to put up.

09:33.500 --> 09:35.670
Want me to help you piss?

09:35.830 --> 09:36.960
Pain in the ass!

09:37.120 --> 09:38.160
Marvin!

09:38.330 --> 09:39.630
You're dead!

09:39.790 --> 09:41.790
Come on, you bastard!

09:59.830 --> 10:01.630
Want some more?

10:02.080 --> 10:04.710
You little commie, come to Daddy!

10:11.250 --> 10:14.880
This is our patch, d'ya understand?

10:19.200 --> 10:23.530
