I said I wasn't sure.

11:54.500 --> 11:56.670
Calm down, guys.

11:59.160 --> 12:00.910
Put your lights on!

12:17.370 --> 12:19.160
- Hey, Grand-Guy.
- Hi.

12:20.660 --> 12:22.780
- What happened?
