12:24.580 --> 12:25.830
- You OK?
- Yeah.

12:26.000 --> 12:27.670
- Who did it?
- Reds.

12:27.830 --> 12:30.250
- Yeah, but who?
- Fuckin' Reds!

12:31.790 --> 12:34.630
- You're bleeding.
- Fuck, I know!

14:08.080 --> 14:11.380
The punks have showed up.
Come on!

14:20.410 --> 14:21.780
Sonovabitch!

14:30.700 --> 14:33.620
Beat him up, beat him up!

14:36.250 --> 14:37.500
Fuckin' Nazis!

14:37.660 --> 14:38.990
Jean-Mi!

14:42.620 --> 14:44.160
Fuck off, you!

14:44.330 --> 14:46.330
I'll kill ya!

14:48.040 --> 14:49.880
Zipper!

14:50.330 --> 14:51.380
Fuckin' skins!

14:51.540 --> 14:54.920
Call an ambulance! Quick!

15:00.250 --> 15:02.210
Look at me, look at me!

15:08.540 --> 15:09.920
Hey, Zipper!

15:16.790 --> 15:21.170
His mother won't let him live with me.
She says I'm too old for him.

15:22.250 --> 15:24.460
She's right, you are!

15:25.660 --> 15:28.240
Maybe in 20 years' time,
but who cares now?

15:32.580 --> 15:34.290
I'll be dead by then.

15:35.580 --> 15:37.250
Don't talk crap.

15:43.580 --> 15:46.380
Do you want to come live with me?

15:47.500 --> 15:49.040
I live above you.

15:49.790 --> 15:51.880
I mean, really live with me.

15:53.040 --> 15:54.380
What about Marvin?

15:55.910 --> 15:58.120
- How'd he take it?
- Badly.

15:58.910 --> 16:00.740
He's so jealous.

16:01.290 --> 16:03.500
You're a real pest!

16:04.250 --> 16:06.040
Behave. No.

16:06.750 --> 16:11.000
Hold him tight
Dirty, salty kisses.

16:11.160 --> 16:15.820
Falling onto the bed
It's a first.

16:16.000 --> 16:20.710
