16:25.200 --> 16:26.990
- Stop it.
- Are you hard?

16:27.160 --> 16:28.410
- Go.
- Why?

16:28.580 --> 16:30.500
- Meet you at Zipper's.
- Why?

16:30.660 --> 16:32.070
