16:41.120 --> 16:42.700
Look who it is.

16:42.870 --> 16:44.320
What do you want?

16:45.290 --> 16:48.130
- Not so brave on your own!
- I'm not on my own.

16:48.290 --> 16:52.250
What's the problem? That little whore?
Is she your chick?

16:52.410 --> 16:55.820
- Not now...
- I'd love to fuck that little bitch.

16:56.450 --> 16:59.950
Or does she prefer being screwed
by Nazis like you?

17:00.830 --> 17:05.250
We don't want you lot. You don't deserve
to be called skinheads.

17:05.410 --> 17:09.160
- You finished?
- We'll never have finished with you!

17:11.200 --> 17:15.069
- We'll do this some other time.
- Stay here, bastard!

17:15.250 --> 17:18.000
- Stop it.
- Stay here, fucker!

17:21.040 --> 17:22.540
What do you want?

17:22.750 --> 17:24.790
What do you want?

17:30.250 --> 17:33.130
Is that what you want, you fucker?

18:56.450 --> 18:58.240
Police! Freeze!

18:58.410 --> 18:59.780
Freeze.

19:16.540 --> 19:17.790
Get in.

19:20.580 --> 19:21.960
Sit here.

19:55.330 --> 19:57.750
Sit down and take off your shoes.

20:28.370 --> 20:29.870
Is he dead?

20:31.830 --> 20:33.000
No.

20:36.290 --> 20:37.670
You're lucky.

20:40.450 --> 20:42.450
But you beat him up badly.

20:43.250 --> 20:44.710
He started it.

20:45.250 --> 20:47.040
What the hell do I care?

20:53.750 --> 20:54.790
Can I have a drink?

20:57.620 --> 20:59.620
Are you a butcher's apprentice?

21:01.750 --> 21:03.130
OK...

21:03.750 --> 21:07.080
What are you? What kind of skinhead?

21:08.120 --> 21:10.700
Which gang? Nazis or reds?

21:13.660 --> 21:15.780
We have better things to do

21:15.950 --> 21:19.120
than deal with assholes like you,
so what are you?

21:26.540 --> 21:27.580
Who's she?

21:28.830 --> 21:30.130
Do you know her?

21:30.830 --> 21:32.380
Is she your girlfriend?

21:32.660 --> 21:34.320
Did you fight over her?

22:34.040 --> 22:35.580
What's your problem?

22:35.750 --> 22:37.460
What're you looking at?

22:38.160 --> 22:38.870
What?

22:39.700 --> 22:42.410
Don't look at me! Fucker!

22:49.540 --> 22:51.170
What're you looking at?

22:51.700 --> 22:53.490
Look at your father!

23:10.830 --> 23:12.170
Get lost.

23:12.870 --> 23:14.070
Get lost!

23:14.450 --> 23:16.200
Filthy race.

23:16.660 --> 23:18.990
Get lost, go on, get lost.

23:30.330 --> 23:31.580
What?

24:21.660 --> 24:24.070
Excuse me, I don't feel good.

24:25.500 --> 24:26.710
What is it?

24:26.870 --> 24:28.070
I don't know.

24:35.160 --> 24:36.570
Have a seat.

24:46.250 --> 24:48.290
You're having trouble breathing?

24:50.160 --> 24:52.570
- Has it happened before?
- No.

25:03.040 --> 25:05.210
You don't have any allergies?

25:05.370 --> 25:06.820
I don't think so.

25:17.250 --> 25:18.460
Take this.

25:26.830 --> 25:28.080
More.

25:30.000 --> 25:34.290
Ah, Mrs. Duteil, I hadn't seen you
today. I missed you!

25:35.790 --> 25:38.040
What's your poison?!

25:45.410 --> 25:47.240
I'll get that for you.

25:50.450 --> 25:51.700
Come with me.

26:12.500 --> 26:14.080
Sit down there.

26:15.040 --> 26:16.920
Wait till it takes effect.

26:18.620 --> 26:20.820
It'll only take about 15 minutes.

26:22.830 --> 26:24.080
Relax.

26:29.040 --> 26:33.250
Read a magazine if you like.
If you don't feel OK, call me.

26:40.580 --> 26:41.960
OK, over to you.

26:59.540 --> 27:01.500
Have you eaten, son?

27:04.040 --> 27:07.750
I kept you some chicken
and peppers, your favorite.

28:41.120 --> 28:42.870
1992

28:43.250 --> 28:44.830
Got a light?

28:50.160 --> 28:51.620
We were waiting for you.

28:55.330 --> 28:57.080
- 'Evening.
- Welcome.

28:57.250 --> 28:59.540
Hello. Happy New Year.

29:02.330 --> 29:03.960
Everything OK?

29:05.540 --> 29:07.500
Was it this quiet last year?

29:07.910 --> 29:09.660
Yeah, I think so.

29:09.830 --> 29:11.540
Happy New Year!

29:12.200 --> 29:15.320
- Happy New Year, man.
- Happy New Year, lovebirds.

29:15.500 --> 29:16.540
- OK?
- Great.

29:16.700 --> 29:18.030
Happy New Year.

29:19.660 --> 29:21.120
Happy New Year.

29:21.290 --> 29:23.000
- Have fun.
- 'Night.

29:24.080 --> 29:25.580
I like them.

29:33.160 --> 29:34.820
Don't touch me!

29:35.750 --> 29:37.580
Who does he think he is?

29:48.830 --> 29:50.290
Asshole.

29:55.160 --> 29:57.450
'Evening, gentlemen.

29:58.080 --> 29:59.330
Hey now.

29:59.500 --> 30:02.460
It's a private party.
Do you have an invitation?

30:02.620 --> 30:04.320
We know Saïd. Let us in.

30:04.830 --> 30:07.790
I don't know Saïd.
You need an invitation.

30:07.950 --> 30:09.820
It's party time. Let us in.

30:10.200 --> 30:12.570
No, you'll have to leave, gentlemen.

30:13.580 --> 30:15.130
What do you want?

30:15.290 --> 30:17.460
You want an invitation?

30:18.250 --> 30:22.250
How's that for an invitation?
Is that OK for you?

30:24.160 --> 30:25.870
What's your problem?

30:26.370 --> 30:28.450
Why are you looking at me like that?

30:30.700 --> 30:32.200
It's OK.

30:33.450 --> 30:34.870
Just you try!

30:45.450 --> 30:47.370
Hello and welcome.

30:47.790 --> 30:49.290
Hey, fucker!

30:52.540 --> 30:53.960
Marco!

30:55.790 --> 30:57.250
Help!

30:58.410 --> 31:01.030
- What happened?
- I don't know.

31:02.540 --> 31:04.080
Oh, fuck!

31:04.250 --> 31:06.790
Call an ambulance. Calou!

31:07.500 --> 31:09.540
- It's OK.
- What is it?

31:09.700 --> 31:12.120
Press on it with your hand!

31:13.870 --> 31:15.120
Stop!

31:15.290 --> 31:17.080
Hold my hand.

31:31.660 --> 31:33.160
Alright, sonny?

31:35.580 --> 31:37.420
You gave me such a fright.

31:39.750 --> 31:41.750
It's OK, Mom, don't worry.

31:45.910 --> 31:47.740
It's alright, Mom.

32:14.410 --> 32:16.530
Is it a boy or a girl?

32:17.000 --> 32:18.670
What's that, sonny?

32:20.620 --> 32:21.870
Nothing.

32:36.950 --> 32:38.950
- Mom...
- Yes?

32:42.750 --> 32:45.880
Did you tell me bedtime stories
when I was little?

32:50.120 --> 32:51.200
Yes.

32:57.500 --> 32:59.210
I don't remember.

33:13.000 --> 33:14.080
Hello, ma'am.

33:14.410 --> 33:15.570
Hello, sir.

33:17.910 --> 33:19.160
So?

33:19.950 --> 33:21.030
How are you?

33:23.080 --> 33:24.330
Why are you here?

33:24.580 --> 33:28.040
The ambulance people called me.
You gave them my name.

33:31.700 --> 33:32.950
Really?

33:53.790 --> 33:55.500
Thanks for coming.

34:00.040 --> 34:01.830
Mom, can I have some water?

34:08.909 --> 34:10.409
Give it to me.

34:19.040 --> 34:20.710
But, in fact,

34:20.870 --> 34:23.120
ladies and gentlemen, the worst thing

34:23.449 --> 34:28.409
is not that this bunch of gangsters
and racketeers line their pockets.

34:28.830 --> 34:30.960
It's shocking for justice,

34:31.699 --> 34:33.320
but still...

34:33.500 --> 34:36.420
The worst thing is,
they're emptying ours.

34:37.250 --> 34:40.920
They leave us defenseless,
without social welfare.

34:41.659 --> 34:43.870
Our grandmothers are killed.

34:44.040 --> 34:48.540
Our storekeepers are murdered,
as happened near here a few days ago.

34:48.699 --> 34:50.239
Need I remind you?

34:51.159 --> 34:53.739
What'll happen if we don't do anything?

34:54.080 --> 34:58.040
How many murders will it take
for them to understand?

34:58.200 --> 35:03.030
Just to understand
that it's always the same people.

35:03.200 --> 35:05.200
It always is.

35:05.370 --> 35:08.950
I'm not afraid to say so.
It's always the blacks

35:09.120 --> 35:11.070
or the Arabs. Sorry, but it is.

35:11.250 --> 35:15.130
I know it's not the done thing
to say that at the moment.

35:15.290 --> 35:18.670
All those mayors who stop us
holding our meetings,

35:18.830 --> 35:22.750
like in Lyon with Michel Noir.
Black by name...!

35:23.700 --> 35:26.490
Or in Grenoble and elsewhere.

35:26.660 --> 35:29.370
All the mayors who claim that our ideas

35:29.540 --> 35:32.920
are crimes, not opinions.

35:33.080 --> 35:36.330
There'll soon be
50 million criminals in France!

35:42.750 --> 35:43.960
France

35:44.120 --> 35:46.780
has a history. So does our party.

35:47.580 --> 35:50.130
We don't have a short memory, us.

35:50.290 --> 35:53.330
France isn't Islam or the Koran.

35:53.500 --> 35:56.630
France isn't Africa.

35:56.790 --> 36:01.080
France is Charlemagne,
Charles Martel, Charles Maurras!

36:01.250 --> 36:05.960
France isn't François Mitterrand
or his prime minister Bérégovoy!

36:06.910 --> 36:10.620
The State has the nerve
to take Jean-Marie Le Pen to court

36:10.790 --> 36:14.000
for incitement to racial hatred.

36:14.450 --> 36:15.620
Imagine that.

36:15.790 --> 36:17.790
What does the State do

36:17.950 --> 36:23.370
when all those North Africans last week
in Nice marched and proclaimed

36:23.540 --> 36:29.040
that they would
"ruin our race and kill us all"?

36:30.450 --> 36:32.740
What can we do in return?

36:32.910 --> 36:35.780
Keep our heads down? Is that it?

36:35.950 --> 36:38.950
Say nothing? Let ourselves be insulted?

36:39.120 --> 36:42.990
Personally, I won't let anyone
insult my country.

36:43.160 --> 36:45.660
I won't let anyone insult our country.

36:45.830 --> 36:47.750
I won't let anyone insult France!

36:52.450 --> 36:56.700
A new order is underway.
The true French must stand up,

36:56.870 --> 37:00.740
as Marshall Pétain stood up,
and have the courage to tell the vermin

37:00.910 --> 37:03.030
that they've had their fun.

37:03.200 --> 37:08.120
It's time they go home or are
sent home with their barbaric religion.

37:08.290 --> 37:13.040
We French must tell them
that this is our home!

37:13.700 --> 37:15.160
Jean-Michel!

37:19.580 --> 37:21.130
My friends,

37:21.290 --> 37:24.380
we all thank
Jean-Michel Cayrol once more.

37:24.540 --> 37:28.880
Let's continue this discussion
less formally

37:29.040 --> 37:32.330
outside where refreshments
will be served.

37:55.370 --> 37:56.700
Excuse me.

37:57.250 --> 38:02.210
Do you think the voting recommendations
will be followed by everyone?

38:02.370 --> 38:03.870
Of course.

38:07.870 --> 38:12.280
Absolutely. Unless agreements
can be made.

38:12.450 --> 38:14.320
You know as well as I do

38:14.500 --> 38:17.920
certain things must be said
at the conference.

38:18.450 --> 38:19.570
For the press.

38:19.750 --> 38:23.830
But you won't consider
standing down for Jacquelin?

38:24.000 --> 38:26.000
Never! I swear.

38:26.160 --> 38:30.280
Between you and me, if I get the chance,
I'll spit in his face.

38:30.450 --> 38:35.740
Like in nature, pests need stamping out.
But don't worry, I won't stand down.

38:35.910 --> 38:39.370
Let's hope so.
That swine should go.

38:44.450 --> 38:46.410
No, stop it!

38:46.700 --> 38:48.240
Stop it!

38:49.160 --> 38:50.370
Hello.

38:51.870 --> 38:53.740
I saw you looking at me.

38:57.000 --> 38:59.830
- I'm Corinne.
- I'm Marc.

39:01.120 --> 39:03.950
- Can you pour me a drink?
- Sure. Red wine?

39:04.120 --> 39:05.620
Yes, alright.

39:10.700 --> 39:11.950
Thanks.

39:12.750 --> 39:14.380
You're not having one?

39:14.540 --> 39:15.750
I am.

39:21.040 --> 39:22.420
Cheers.

39:23.120 --> 39:24.570
Is that for me?

39:29.580 --> 39:30.960
Are you local?

39:31.120 --> 39:33.780
Not really. I live in Corbeil.

39:34.750 --> 39:37.170
My uncle organized the meeting.

39:37.700 --> 39:39.160
This is his house.

