01:12:32.830 --> 01:12:34.210
Thanks.

01:12:54.910 --> 01:12:59.740
Hey, pal, can you help me unload?
There are 14 more to do.

01:13:01.330 --> 01:13:03.290
- OK.
- Thanks.

01:13:04.750 --> 01:13:06.380
God will repay you.

01:13:10.830 --> 01:13:13.500
- Do you come here often?
- No.

01:14:02.370 --> 01:14:03.780
I don't understand.

01:14:05.950 --> 01:14:09.030
I did everything.
There shouldn't be a problem.

01:14:09.200 --> 01:14:12.910
I know you're doing your best,
but I told you already

01:14:13.080 --> 01:14:15.460
we've done everything we could.

01:14:15.790 --> 01:14:18.040
Your criminal record didn't help.

01:14:18.450 --> 01:14:21.910
I know you've changed, Marc.
I understand you're upset.

01:14:22.540 --> 01:14:24.630
But the kid refuses to see you.

01:14:27.330 --> 01:14:30.380
Can't I even call her? Talk to her?

01:14:30.540 --> 01:14:34.630
No, don't. You have to wait
for her to grow up.

01:14:35.330 --> 01:14:40.670
We'll apply again next year
and the year after. She's only little.

01:14:42.870 --> 01:14:46.450
I agree, her family environment
doesn't help,

01:14:46.620 --> 01:14:51.780
but she'll soon be a teenager.
The judge might change his mind.

01:14:52.290 --> 01:14:53.830
You have to be patient.

01:14:59.410 --> 01:15:02.530
Thank you, ma'am. Sorry.

01:15:02.700 --> 01:15:04.200
What do I owe you?

01:15:05.450 --> 01:15:08.780
Nothing. I haven't done anything.
You owe me nothing.

01:15:16.330 --> 01:15:17.670
Mom...

01:15:18.540 --> 01:15:20.790
Mom... Come eat.

01:15:22.290 --> 01:15:27.080
This morning, a 30-year-old man
was released due to lack of evidence.

01:15:27.250 --> 01:15:29.040
Now, politics.

01:15:29.200 --> 01:15:33.030
After a heated conference
before the European elections,

01:15:33.200 --> 01:15:37.530
disagreement within the Front National
seems far from over.

01:15:37.700 --> 01:15:42.280
The far right is divided once again.
There are no holds barred.

01:15:42.500 --> 01:15:46.420
Here is our special report.

01:15:46.580 --> 01:15:50.380
The party has decided
to turn over a new leaf.

01:15:50.540 --> 01:15:51.790
Marc!

01:15:54.200 --> 01:15:56.160
But I haven't forgotten.

01:15:56.660 --> 01:16:01.320
I know where we come from,
who we are and always will be.

01:16:02.200 --> 01:16:07.620
I'm not ashamed of my convictions.
I won't hide them or pretend,

01:16:07.870 --> 01:16:12.070
like many of my comrades
who've let their hair grow

01:16:12.370 --> 01:16:16.570
and who now wear suits and ties
in the Central Committee.

01:16:17.000 --> 01:16:19.920
But the voters aren't fooled,
believe me.

01:16:20.080 --> 01:16:23.540
I'm not a whore,
if you'll pardon the expression.

01:16:23.700 --> 01:16:25.070
Thanks, sonny.

01:16:25.250 --> 01:16:27.580
I won't sell out to become mayor.

01:16:27.750 --> 01:16:32.080
After the announcement
of Jean-Michel Cayrol's suspension,

01:16:32.250 --> 01:16:34.580
he made barely veiled threats.

01:16:34.750 --> 01:16:36.710
But at party headquarters,

01:16:36.870 --> 01:16:39.820
there is talk of secret alliances...

01:16:53.040 --> 01:16:54.540
Eat up, it'll go cold.

01:17:14.500 --> 01:17:18.880
A happy Sunday with Jérémie Kisling
and his "Rendez-vous Courtois"

01:17:19.040 --> 01:17:22.630
from his latest album.
To forget the rain,

01:17:22.790 --> 01:17:27.540
what better than a laugh
with the classic "Arab Cop" sketch?

01:17:27.700 --> 01:17:29.780
Over to Coluche...

01:18:07.410 --> 01:18:10.030
Gwendoline, can you get your brother?

01:19:43.410 --> 01:19:44.780
Who is it?

01:19:45.700 --> 01:19:47.200
It's Marco.

01:19:50.540 --> 01:19:51.960
He's come to see you.

01:19:54.330 --> 01:19:56.460
That's good. I'm pleased.

01:20:21.580 --> 01:20:23.000
He can't see.

01:20:42.080 --> 01:20:44.960
They say he's dun for.

01:20:51.250 --> 01:20:53.040
You writing again?

01:20:54.080 --> 01:20:55.290
No.

01:21:07.790 --> 01:21:10.750
She makes as many mistakes
as a 5-year-old!

01:21:10.910 --> 01:21:12.660
So I see!

01:21:12.910 --> 01:21:14.240
Cut it out!

01:21:15.160 --> 01:21:19.620
Screw the pair of you!
You've ruined my life for long enough!

01:21:58.700 --> 01:22:00.450
Sure it's a good idea?

01:22:03.080 --> 01:22:05.040
What difference does it make?

01:22:21.660 --> 01:22:22.950
You OK?

01:22:23.200 --> 01:22:25.120
I'm good, don't worry.

01:22:25.700 --> 01:22:27.570
Is your job going OK?

01:22:27.750 --> 01:22:28.880
Yeah.

01:22:29.290 --> 01:22:31.500
That's good. I'm pleased.

01:22:33.910 --> 01:22:37.660
My sister offered me a job
in a bar in Grenoble.

01:23:08.830 --> 01:23:10.130
You know...

01:23:13.580 --> 01:23:15.290
I'm not scared...

01:23:17.700 --> 01:23:19.320
I'm not scared.

01:23:28.120 --> 01:23:30.280
Sorry, it's time to wash him.

01:23:30.540 --> 01:23:32.040
No problem.

01:23:32.410 --> 01:23:35.280
I'll be back. I'll be right outside.

01:23:36.000 --> 01:23:38.960
- I'll help you.
- What did I tell you?

01:23:39.330 --> 01:23:41.750
That's nothing. Nothing at all.

01:23:41.910 --> 01:23:44.820
Take that out.
It's not allowed in the rooms.

01:23:51.580 --> 01:23:54.830
I'll be back. I'll be right outside.

01:24:31.580 --> 01:24:33.920
- Here you are.
- Careful, it's hot.

01:24:41.450 --> 01:24:44.030
Hey, handsome. You OK, Pascal?

01:24:44.200 --> 01:24:45.870
How's it going?

01:24:48.290 --> 01:24:49.380
Here.

01:24:52.120 --> 01:24:54.370
Let's set this up.

01:24:56.660 --> 01:25:00.280
1st, 2nd, 3rd generation.

01:25:01.000 --> 01:25:04.130
We're all pork eaters!

01:25:04.290 --> 01:25:08.000
1st, 2nd, 3rd generation.

01:25:08.160 --> 01:25:10.410
We're all pork eaters!

01:25:11.200 --> 01:25:12.620
Come here.

01:25:15.910 --> 01:25:21.120
Step right up. Don't be scared.
We're not here to be provocative.

01:25:21.750 --> 01:25:24.170
No, we're here, because some of you

01:25:24.330 --> 01:25:28.000
are sleeping rough,
some of you are hungry.

01:25:28.160 --> 01:25:33.280
Well, we've made you
a delicious, nourishing meal.

01:25:33.790 --> 01:25:35.080
That's all.

01:25:35.250 --> 01:25:39.630
Everything else
that people say about us is just lies.

01:25:40.580 --> 01:25:45.000
In fact, the law courts allowed us
to serve this French soup.

01:25:45.620 --> 01:25:49.030
I don't see why
or on what grounds

01:25:49.200 --> 01:25:52.370
a nationalist group like ours
should obey

01:25:52.540 --> 01:25:56.000
the rules of the Muslim
or Jewish religions.

01:25:57.540 --> 01:25:59.170
I seem to recall

01:25:59.330 --> 01:26:04.000
that Church and State are separate.
We won't be dictated to by Islamists!

01:26:04.160 --> 01:26:05.870
Shame on you! Go away!

01:26:06.040 --> 01:26:07.830
Who said that?

01:26:08.000 --> 01:26:09.790
Shame on us?

01:26:10.870 --> 01:26:13.120
For feeding people who are hungry?

01:26:15.410 --> 01:26:18.240
Do you even know what pork soup is?

01:26:18.660 --> 01:26:23.450
It's what French soldiers ate
in World War I for 4 years.

01:26:24.200 --> 01:26:27.660
Pork soup is part
of this country's history.

01:26:29.540 --> 01:26:32.080
What will happen to pork farmers?

01:26:32.250 --> 01:26:35.460
Do we put them in camps
or exterminate them?

01:26:41.870 --> 01:26:43.950
Turn the camera off.

01:26:45.580 --> 01:26:49.040
Red, white and blue!
France for the French!

01:26:55.750 --> 01:26:57.130
Why are you here?

01:26:58.330 --> 01:27:00.790
Same as you,
I'm giving out soup.

01:27:04.290 --> 01:27:05.540
I'll be right back.

01:27:25.540 --> 01:27:28.130
How can you look
at yourself in a mirror?

01:27:32.250 --> 01:27:34.790
I heard you'd sunk low...

01:27:36.080 --> 01:27:37.920
I wouldn't have believed it.

01:27:38.500 --> 01:27:41.000
I want you lot
to take your things and go.

01:27:42.910 --> 01:27:45.700
- You giving me orders?
- No.

01:27:46.450 --> 01:27:48.120
Go away. They're hungry.

01:27:48.290 --> 01:27:50.000
How could you?

01:27:51.500 --> 01:27:53.130
How could you betray us?

01:27:55.950 --> 01:27:58.990
You belong in front of a firing squad.

01:27:59.700 --> 01:28:01.660
I want to smash your face in!

01:28:01.830 --> 01:28:03.790
Go ahead. Then go.

01:28:06.250 --> 01:28:07.920
I'm asking as a friend.

01:28:10.160 --> 01:28:11.320
A friend?

01:28:19.750 --> 01:28:21.000
Stop it! They can see you!

01:28:22.000 --> 01:28:23.080
Leave him alone.

01:28:24.370 --> 01:28:26.410
- Pack up and go.
- But...

01:28:26.580 --> 01:28:27.710
Take all that!

01:28:27.950 --> 01:28:28.950
Let's go.

01:28:29.120 --> 01:28:32.320
C'mon, guys, let's pack up and go!

01:28:44.950 --> 01:28:46.490
- OK, Marc?
- Yeah.

01:28:46.660 --> 01:28:49.700
- We'll report it to the police...
- No need.

01:28:49.870 --> 01:28:51.700
- You're bleeding.
- It's OK.

01:28:51.870 --> 01:28:54.910
It's all over, it's alright.
Thanks.

01:29:19.500 --> 01:29:21.040
Ready, gentlemen?

01:29:36.000 --> 01:29:40.210
- We're gathered here for Yvette...
- Excuse me.

01:29:40.370 --> 01:29:43.570
There's no need. No-one's here.

01:30:10.160 --> 01:30:11.740
Thank you, gentlemen.

01:30:16.830 --> 01:30:18.630
Sorry I'm late, kid.

01:30:19.000 --> 01:30:20.290
It doesn't matter.

01:30:22.660 --> 01:30:24.160
I'm pleased to see you.

01:30:28.660 --> 01:30:29.950
Gentlemen...

01:30:47.700 --> 01:30:52.450
They've come from all over France
to say no to same-sex marriage.

01:30:52.620 --> 01:30:58.740
340,000 people according to the police,
a million according to the organizers.

01:30:58.910 --> 01:31:02.740
There were families
with up to 3 generations present.

01:31:02.910 --> 01:31:06.870
I'm pleased to be demonstrating
with my grandchildren

01:31:07.040 --> 01:31:08.790
to defend the family.

01:31:08.950 --> 01:31:11.530
Children need a mother and father.

01:31:11.700 --> 01:31:14.570
It's only natural
we're demonstrating today.

01:31:14.750 --> 01:31:18.040
A family is
a mother, a father, and children.

01:31:18.200 --> 01:31:21.240
3 processions converged
on the Eiffel Tower

01:31:21.410 --> 01:31:24.870
in a light-hearted mood
with carefully considered slogans

01:31:25.040 --> 01:31:28.540
which avoided any homophobic messages.

01:31:29.000 --> 01:31:32.000
We have gay friends,
we adore them,

01:31:32.160 --> 01:31:35.450
but you need a mother and father
to make a baby.

01:31:35.620 --> 01:31:38.070
The demonstration of strength
was successful

01:31:38.250 --> 01:31:42.420
with the crowd's support along the way.

01:31:42.580 --> 01:31:45.960
The bells are ringing,
but it's not a religious event.

01:31:46.540 --> 01:31:50.790
A 4th procession appeared uninvited.

01:31:50.950 --> 01:31:53.240
1,000 hard-line Catholics

01:31:53.410 --> 01:31:58.120
whose presence was unwelcome
were kept away.

01:32:08.750 --> 01:32:12.830
Also kept away,
right and far-right politicians

01:32:13.000 --> 01:32:17.170
came to demonstrate,
even though not all were present.

01:32:36.450 --> 01:32:38.280
The latest polls show

01:32:38.450 --> 01:32:43.320
that over half the French are
in favor of same-sex marriage.

01:32:50.500 --> 01:32:55.250
France is at war
with terrorism in Mali

01:32:55.410 --> 01:32:58.160
to maintain our ally's security...

